package Doubt_Class_1;

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Print_Prime {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
		int n = sc.nextInt();
		for (int i = 2; i <= n; i++) {

			int fact = 0;
			for (int j = 2; j <i; j++) {

				if (i % j == 0) {
					fact++;
					break;

				}

			}

			if (fact == 0) {
				System.out.println(i);
			}

		}

	}

}
